  "text": "According to [CITATION_1] or to [CITATION_2] , the developmental events leading to anther formation and pollen release are exquisitely timed and choreographed. According to the same authors, cell differentiation and dehiscence events occur in a precise chronological order which correlates with size of floral bud.",
